00\",\"DVT\":null,\"name_jp\":\"\\uff8f\\uff99\\uff7a\\uff92 \\u4e00\\u4f11\\u3055\\u3093 1KG\",\"description_vi\":\"\",\"description_en\":\"\",\"origin_id\":\"1\",\"volume_vi\":\"1Kg\",\"volume_jp\":null,\"volume_en\":null,\"image_id\":\"94\",\"order\":\"0\",\"name_vi\":\"\\u0110\\u1eadu t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng l\\u00ean men Ikkyu-san Marukome \",\"name_en\":\"IKKYU SAN 1KG MARUKOME\",\"description_jp\":\"\",\"guide_vi\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align: left;\\\">- D&ugrave;ng ch\\u1ebf bi\\u1ebfn m&oacute;n s&uacute;p miso, c&aacute;c m&oacute;n l\\u1ea9u.&nbsp;<\\/p><p style=\\\"text-align: left;\\\"><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.foodzone.vn\\/index\\/category\\/68\\\">Tham kh\\u1ea3o chi ti\\u1ebft c&aacute;ch n\\u1ea5u s&uacute;p miso.<\\/a><\\/p><p><img class=\\\"fr-dib fr-draggable\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.foodzone.vn\\/public\\/uploads\\/2020-05-21\\/1590045850.jpg\\\" style=\\\"width: 447px; height: 298px;\\\"><\\/p>\",\"guide_en\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><a allowfullscreen=\\\"\\\" frameborder=\\\"0\\\" height=\\\"315\\\" href=\\\"\\\" src=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/HhlrjVFRwj0\\\"><\\/a><\\/p><p>- Use to make miso soup, hotpot.<\\/p><p><a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.foodzone.vn\\/index\\/category\\/68\\\">Detailed reference for Miso soup.<\\/a><\\/p><p><img class=\\\"fr-dib fr-draggable\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.foodzone.vn\\/public\\/uploads\\/2020-05-21\\/1590045994.jpg\\\" style=\\\"width: 431px; height: 287.333px;\\\"><\\/p>\",\"guide_jp\":\"\",\"detail_vi\":\"<p style=\\\"text-align: justify;\\\">\\u0110\\u1eadu t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng l&ecirc;n men (Miso) l&agrave; m\\u1ed9t trong nh\\u1eefng lo\\u1ea1i t\\u01b0\\u01a1ng quan tr\\u1ecdng nh\\u1ea5t c\\u1ee7a v&ugrave;ng \\u0110&ocirc;ng Nam &Aacute;. \\u1ede Nh\\u1eadt h\\u01a1n 90% d&acirc;n s\\u1ed1 b\\u1eaft \\u0111\\u1ea7u m\\u1ed9t ng&agrave;y m\\u1edbi b\\u1eb1ng m\\u1ed9t c\\u1ed1c s&uacute;p miso n&oacute;ng b\\u1ed5 d\\u01b0\\u1ee1ng, t\\u0103ng s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe thay v&igrave; u