www.foodzone.vn\\/public\\/uploads\\/2020-05-25\\/1590394745.jpg\\\" style=\\\"width: 408px; height: 350.02px;\\\"><\\/p><p>D&ugrave;ng \\u0111\\u1ec3 n\\u1ea5u n\\u01b0\\u1edbc dashi, n\\u1ea5u b\\u1ed9t cho b&eacute; \\u0103n d\\u1eb7m.<\\/p><p>T\\u1ea5m Kombu d&agrave;y v&agrave; dai n&ecirc;n khi ninh n\\u1ea5u c&aacute;c m&oacute;n \\u0103n, v\\u1eabn c&oacute; th\\u1ec3 s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng c\\u1ea3 n\\u01b0\\u1edbc ng\\u1ecdt v&agrave; c\\u1ea3 x&aacute;c Kombu \\u0111\\u1ec3 x&agrave;o c&ugrave;ng v\\u1edbi c&aacute;c th\\u1ef1c ph\\u1ea9m kh&aacute;c m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng b\\u1ecb n&aacute;t hay bi\\u1ebfn \\u0111\\u1ed5i m&agrave;u s\\u1eafc. M&ugrave;i v\\u1ecb t\\u1ef1 nhi&ecirc;n, kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; v\\u1ecb tanh \\u0111\\u1eb7c tr\\u01b0ng nh\\u01b0 c&aacute;c lo\\u1ea1i rong bi\\u1ec3n kh&aacute;c n&ecirc;n c&oacute; th\\u1ec3 d&ugrave;ng cho nh\\u1eefng ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi b\\u1eaft \\u0111\\u1ea7u s\\u1eed d\\u1ee5ng rong bi\\u1ec3n ho\\u1eb7c kh&ocirc;ng quen v\\u1edbi v\\u1ecb tanh c\\u1ee7a rong bi\\u1ec3n.<span>&nbsp;<\\/span><\\/p><p>Ngo&agrave;i ra, c\\u0169ng c&oacute; th\\u1ec3 th\\u01b0\\u1edfng th\\u1ee9c nh\\u01b0 m\\u1ed9t topping \\u0103n k&egrave;m v\\u1edbi c\\u01a1m v&agrave; c&aacute;c m&oacute;n \\u0103n theo s\\u1edf th&iacute;ch.<\\/p><p><img class=\\\"fr-dib fr-draggable\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.foodzone.vn\\/public\\/uploads\\/2020-05-25\\/1590394733.jpg\\\" style=\\\"width: 408px; height: 272px;\\\"><\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\",\"guide_en\":\"<p><img class=\\\"fr-dib fr-draggable\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.foodzone.vn\\/public\\/uploads\\/2020-05-25\\/1590394640.jpg\\\" style=\\\"width: 472px; height: 315.333px;\\\"><\\/p><p>Used to cook dashi water, cook baby food for miles.<\\/p><p>Kombu plate is thick and chewy, so when cooking dishes, you can still use both fresh water and Kombu corpse to fry along with other foods without getting crushed or changing colors. Natural taste, no specific fishy taste like other types of seaweed, so it can be used for people who start using seaweed or not familiar with the fishy taste of seaweed.<\\/p><p>In addition, it can also be enjoyed as a topping served with rice and dishes of interest.<\\/p><p><img class=\\\"fr-dib fr-draggable\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.foodzone.vn\\/public\\/uploads\\/2020-05-25\\/1590394653.jpg\\\" style=\\\"width: 484px; height: 416.985px;\\\"><\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\",\"guide_jp\":\"\",\"detail_vi\":\"<p>Rong bi\\u1ec3n s\\u1ee3i Tororo \\u0111\\u01b0\\u1ee3c l&agrave;m t\\u1eeb t\\u1ea3o b\\u1eb9 Kombu r\\u1ea5t gi&agrave;u ch\\u1ea5t s\\u1eaft, ch\\u1ea5t x\\u01a1, canxi, kho&aacute;ng ch\\u1ea5t, acid amin t\\u1ed1t cho s\\u1ee9c kh\\u1ecfe.<\\/p><p>Ch\\u1ee9a Fucoidan gi&uacute;p ch\\u1ed1ng oxi h&oacute;a, ph&ograve;ng ch\\u1ed1ng ung th\\u01b0, t\\u0103ng c\\u01b0\\u1eddng h\\u1ec7 mi\\u1ec5n d\\u1ecbch.<\\/p><p>Gi\\u1ea3m cholesterol, t\\u1ed1t cho tim m\\u1ea1ch &amp; ti&ecirc;u h&oacute;a.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\",\"detail_en\":\"<p>Tororo seaweed is made from kombu kelp which is rich in iron, fiber, calcium, minerals, amino acids that are good for health.<\\/p><p>Contains Fucoidan to help prevent oxidation, prevent cancer, boost the immune system.<\\/p><p>Reduce cholesterol, good for cardiovascular &amp; digestive.<\\/p>\",\"detail_jp\":\"\",\"element_vi\":\"<p>Konbu.<\\/p>\",\"element_en\":\"<p>Konbu<\\/p>\",\"element_jp\":\"\",\"date\":\"2020-05-25 14:09:45\",\"active\":\"1\",\"expiry_date\":null,\"preservation_id\":\"1\",\"deleted\":\"0\",\"units\":null,\"image\":{\"id\":\"1111\",\"name\":null,\"date\":null,\"src\":\"\\/upload\\/images\\/637213390300444595DS057.jpg\",\"user_id\":null,\"deleted\":\"0\",\"size\":null,\"file_type\":null,\"real_name\":null,\"type\":\"2\"},\"price_km\":null,\"qty\":1,\"unit_id\":0,\"amount\":218000}');

